&lt;p&gt;Change your query as below. If you only want data from first table then no need join query only use inner query&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;select DISTINCT u.ID, u.user_nicename from wp_users u WHERE u.ID not in 
